      • isTree

        private boolean isTree(java.util.IdentityHashMap<SimpleLTL,SimpleLTL> seen)
        Recursive function for checking if this SimpleLTL structure is a tree, i.e., not a directed acyclical graph (DAG) where sharing of subtrees is allowed. The already seen SimpleLTL subtrees are tracked in seen.

      • renameAP

        public void renameAP(java.lang.String prefixFrom,
                     java.lang.String prefixTo)
        Renames the atomic propositions apparing in the formula that start with prefixFrom. For these, the prefix is replaced by prefixTo. For example, with prefixFrom = "L" and prefixTo = "p", "L3" will be renamed to "p3", but "T2" will be left as-is.
